      "updated": 1779222194470,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mission 07 target architecture\nObservability: every /query and /briefing must return a safe trace_id. Langfuse Cloud if configured; otherwise local fallback.\nEvals: offline deterministic runner with precision@k, JSON validity, ontology mapping, groundedness judge, coordination caution, latency/cost, export JSON.\nNever log full docs, full prompts, full responses, headers, stack traces or secrets.",
      "originalText": "Mission 07 target architecture\nObservability: every /query and /briefing must return a safe trace_id. Langfuse Cloud if configured; otherwise local fallback.\nEvals: offline deterministic runner with precision@k, JSON validity, ontology mapping, groundedness judge, coordination caution, latency/cost, export JSON.\nNever log full docs, full prompts, full responses, headers, stack traces or secrets.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": null,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
