      "text": "Security\nNo real .env in git\nNo API keys in code/docs\nNo headers/secrets/stack traces in logs,\nerrors, traces or eval outputs",
      "originalText": "Security\nNo real .env in git\nNo API keys in code/docs\nNo headers/secrets/stack traces in logs,\nerrors, traces or eval outputs",
